key_0.comment:
*this is the date and location given.
 
Strange listen.

Worth it for the Franklin's Tower which Jerry refuses to let die,
otherwise its pretty painful.

There was a decent amount of hiss which given the rehearsal
nature of the recording is distraction.
XNoise did an adequate job at minimal settings.

Thanks to M.Townshend for sharing his cassette source.
